### PART 6: Typography Fix

Replace all raw px font sizes with a consistent scale:

| Current | Replace With | Tailwind Class |
|---------|-------------|----------------|
| `text-[9px]` | 10px | `text-[10px]` (group labels only) |
| `text-[11px]` | 11px | keep for meta/helper text |
| `text-[13px]` | 13px | `text-sm` |
| `text-[15px]` | 15px | `text-base` |
| `text-[18px]` | 18px | `text-lg` |

Use `font-medium` (500) for section titles, `font-normal` (400) for preview text, `font-semibold` (600) for header titles.

---

### PART 7: Color Semantic Clarity

The red accent `#b91c1c` is overused. Assign semantic roles:

| Role | Color | Usage |
|------|-------|-------|
| **Primary CTA** | `#b91c1c` (red-700) | Export PDF button ONLY |
| **Interactive accent** | Use `themeColor` variable | Active states, focus rings |
| **Done / Success** | `#10b981` (emerald-500) | Completion indicators |
| **Warning / Unsaved** | `#f59e0b` (amber-500) | Cloud status |
| **Muted text** | `#71717a` (zinc-500) | Subtitles, helpers |
| **Body text** | `#e4e4e7` (zinc-200) | Section titles |

